```
"Invalid: data.postal_code should match pattern \"[A-Z][0-9‚Ä¶A-Z] [0-9][A-Z][0-9]\", data should match \"else\" schema"
```

## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction
* `schematics blank --name=hello-world`
* `cd hello-world`
* `npm i`
* `touch src/hello-world/schema.json` and copy:
   ```
   {
     "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/schema",
     "id": "hello-world",
     "type": "object",
     "properties": {
       "street_address": {
         "type": "string"
       },
